   \alpha  & 2 & \gamma   \cr 
   \beta  & 1 & 0  \cr 
   { - 1} & 0 & 1  \cr 

 } } \right| = \alpha  - 2\beta  + \gamma  = 1$$ [समीकरण (iv) से]

